Comments
Gear supports single and multi-line comments.  Multi-line comments can nest, but they must be balanced.  Blanced means that for every opening comment there is a corresponding closing comment.
# This is a single line comment.

The example below demonstrates a multi-line comment with a nested multi-line comment.
#{
    This is a
       multi-line comment

    #{ This is a nested 
       multi-line comment #}
#}
